data.description: **GREAT OPPORTUNITY! 2.6% INTEREST RATE MORTGAGE IS ASSUMABLE! APPROX $1,000/MONTH IN INTEREST SAVINGS BY NEW BUYERS!!!** Welcome to this spacious WATERFRONT POOL home located in desirable SE Cape Coral. Brand NEW ROOF 2023 and brand NEW POOL CAGE 2023. This home features 4 large bedrooms, 2.5 baths and 2 car garage. No bedrooms share a wall making it perfect for privacy. Fully remodeled kitchen with beautiful granite and stainless steel appliances. Large covered lanai and wet bar, perfect for entertaining guests poolside. The master bedroom offers a serene oasis with its ensuite bathroom, walk-in closet and view of the canal and pool area. New wood flooring in all 4 bedrooms. Completely fenced-in oversized TRIPLE LOT offers lots of privacy and room for kids or animals to play. NEW FENCE 2023. This spacious lot is located on a peaceful freshwater canal with direct access to several large lakes and canal system. Live the Florida lifestyle by fishing, boating or kayaking right off your backyard. Quiet neighborhood close to shopping, restaurants, schools and hospital. All assessments in & paid in full. NO FLOOD insurance required. See complete list of updates in supplements.
